nothing.

33:29.741 --> 33:32.010 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: You didn't
think it would
work.

33:32.043 --> 33:33.712 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
INNA SIMONE: Absolutely not.

33:33.745 --> 33:38.516 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: But, later
that day, the
hackers released her files in
full.

33:38.550 --> 33:48.226 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
For the "PBS NewsHour," I'm
