44:06.878 --> 44:08.279 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
these days.

44:08.312 --> 44:09.380 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Jeffrey Brown has more.

44:09.413 --> 44:12.984 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
MORGAN FREEMAN, Actor: The Oscar
goes to "Spotlight."

44:13.017 --> 44:20.057 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: The winner was
something of
a surprise: "Spotlight," a film
about one

44:20.091 --> 44:26.697 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
