44:28.533 --> 44:30.301 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
TOM MCCARTHY, Director,
"Spotlight": We made
this film for all the
journalists who have

44:30.334 --> 44:35.406 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
