courage and will

44:35.439 --> 44:40.611 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
to overcome is really an
inspiration to all.
We have to do to make sure this
never happens

44:40.645 --> 44:42.446 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
again.

44:42.480 --> 44:44.248 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
RACHEL MCADAMS, Actress: The
