indicate that there were senior
clergy involved.

44:44.282 --> 44:48.085 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: The film recounts
how Globe
reporters and editors tracked
down cases of

44:48.119 --> 44:53.658 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
