positions.

44:57.128 --> 45:03.000 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The paper's "Spotlight" team
tracked over
900 active and retired priests,
finding some

45:03.034 --> 45:06.571 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
