45:06.604 --> 45:11.809 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LIEV SCHREIBER, Actor: We need
to focus on
the institution, not the
individual priests.

45:11.842 --> 45:16.380 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Practice and policy. Show me the
church manipulated
the system so that these guys
wouldn't have

45:16.414 --> 45:21.118 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
to face charges. Show me they
put those same
priests back into parishes time
and time again.

45:21.152 --> 45:23.921 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Show me this was systemic, that
it came form
the top down.

45:23.955 --> 45:28.125 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Actor Liev
Schreiber®MD-BO /
played the Globe's editor,
Martin Baron.

45:28.159 --> 45:31.395 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LIEV SCHREIBER: When Tom sent me
the script,
I called him immediately and I
said, this

45:31.429 --> 45:35.967 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
is such an amazing piece and
