and so important that we
remember what an

45:36.000 --> 45:39.270 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
asset this is to an asset to our
society and
our culture and our democracy.

45:39.303 --> 45:44.875 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: In 2002, as the
original investigation
was still unfolding, the
"NewsHour" visited

45:44.909 --> 45:46.711 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
the Globe newsroom.

45:46.744 --> 45:51.549 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The real Martin Baron spoke of
how the case
