46:05.329 --> 46:08.032 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Baron is now
editor of The
Washington Post.

46:08.065 --> 46:13.004 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
When we spoke to him this fall
