47:02.787 --> 47:07.291 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We're joined now by Margaret
Sullivan, outgoing
public editor for The New York
Times. She

47:07.324 --> 47:12.063 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
