Engelberg,

47:12.096 --> 47:17.968 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
the editor in chief of
ProPublica, a nonprofit
news organization that has won
numerous awards

47:18.002 --> 47:19.470 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
for its investigative work.

47:19.503 --> 47:20.604 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Welcome, both, to you.

47:20.638 --> 47:22.406 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Margaret Sullivan, let me start
with you.

47:22.440 --> 47:26.677 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
You wrote recently that -- quote
-- "The film
'Spotlight' is powerful and
moving, but it

47:26.711 --> 47:32.083 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
