48:07.384 --> 48:10.387 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
STEPHEN ENGELBERG, Editor in
Chief, ProPublica:
Well, it's very interesting,
because right

48:10.421 --> 48:16.193 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
