49:00.271 --> 49:04.775 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And so newspapers which made
money by charging
for subscription and ads find
their ad revenues

49:04.809 --> 49:09.880 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
severely pitched and
subscription revenues
evaporating. And in the face of
that, people

49:09.914 --> 49:14.051 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
want to go online and read this
wonderful
content for free. That is not a
model that

49:14.084 --> 49:15.920 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
works.

49:15.953 --> 49:19.490 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
On the other side of it, though,
it is literally
amazing. I started in the
business when they

49:19.523 --> 49:23.761 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
still had typewriters, believe
it or not,
and it's literally amazing these
days what

49:23.794 --> 49:29.099 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
you can access in terms of data,
in terms
of journal articles,
information, finding

49:29.133 --> 49:31.068 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
people.

49:31.101 --> 49:33.838 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Everything you want to do as an
investigative
reporter is just enhanced by the
current technology.

49:33.871 --> 49:38.876 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
JEFFREY BROWN: Well, so,
Margaret Sullivan,
if I ask you, is "Spotlight"
possible today,

49:38.909 --> 49:42.246 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
