some cases yes,
but in a lot of cases no.

49:42.279 --> 49:47.618 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MARGARET SULLIVAN: I think it is
still possible
in most places.

49:47.651 --> 49:52.590 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But I think that the will to do
this kind
of work is weakening somewhat,
and it has

49:52.623 --> 49:58.529 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
to be beefed up. "Spotlight" is
such an inspiring
movie, that I'm hopeful that it
will cause

49:58.562 --> 50:04.134 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
owners and editors and
publishers to realize
just how important this work is
and to fund

50:04.168 --> 50:05.903 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
it and to get behind it.

50:05.936 --> 50:11.809 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Tell us, what
kind of stories
do you fear are being missed
even today?

50:11.842 --> 50:14.745 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MARGARET SULLIVAN: Well, it's
