to know what's being missed...

50:14.778 --> 50:16.580 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Of course.

50:16.614 --> 50:18.949 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MARGARET SULLIVAN: ... because
you don't know
it until you read it in the
paper or hear

50:18.983 --> 50:20.751 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
it or watch it.

50:20.784 --> 50:25.623 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But the stories that are really
difficult
to do are the ones that are so
time-consuming.

50:25.656 --> 50:29.526 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
And you could tell from
"Spotlight" that people
were knocking on doors and they
were going

50:29.560 --> 50:33.998 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
