agonizing about how
to nail it down.

50:34.031 --> 50:38.435 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And those kind of things are
very expensive
and they take time. But it is
the stories

50:38.469 --> 50:43.540 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
about holding powerful people
and institutions
accountable that really, really
matter.

50:43.574 --> 50:49.380 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Steve Engelberg,
