of it.

51:04.094 --> 51:06.330 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
STEPHEN ENGELBERG: Well, the
model doesn't
really change what you can do.

51:06.363 --> 51:10.868 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
In the old days, you had
advertiser who gave
a lot of money. And, of course,
you know,

51:10.901 --> 51:15.372 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
