journalists are around?

51:48.439 --> 51:50.274 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
That's a pretty basic story.

51:50.307 --> 51:55.612 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Well, Margaret
